Read the ``Getting Started'' Chapter of the PETSc manual:

  https://petsc.org/release/manual/getting_started/

In particular, the section on developing an application program that uses PETSc:

  https://petsc.org/release/manual/getting_started/#writing-c-c-or-fortran-applications

For instance, ex2

  https://petsc.org/release/src/ksp/ksp/tutorials/ex2.c.html

or ex29

  https://petsc.org/release/src/ksp/ksp/tutorials/ex29.c.html

could be of interest.
